incident_updates.body: We have determined the origin of the incident affecting our .DK Domains offer, customers in the impacted zone are unable to perform some tasks on .DK domains. Here are some supplementary details : Start time : 06/11/2025 12:53 UTC Impacted Service(s) : Multiple operations (Registration, Renew, Transfer, Restore, Delete) are temporarily unavailable for .DK domains. Customers Impact : Customers are temporarily unable to perform specified operations on .DK domains. Root Cause : This incident is caused by a maintenance of one of our provider. Ongoing Actions : The incident has been identified and our teams are mobilised to restore service as quickly as possible.
